# Client Conventions

- Copy from starter-template when creating new clients; only change site.config.ts and .env.local
- No cross-client imports; no hardcoded client values in components
- Run `pnpm validate-client clients/<path>` before commit
- Starter template: port 3101; use `pnpm --filter @clients/starter-template dev`
